AMIGO TECHNOLOGY May Sales Fall 36.27% (Table) : 6241 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-06-10T03:23:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/amigo-technology-may-sales-fall-36-27-table-6241-tt.html
AMIGO TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 36.27% to NT$20,275,000 from NT$31,814,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2011           5/2010
Sales             20,275           31,814    
YOY%             -36.27%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            113,751          124,778    
YOY%              -8.84% 
=================================================================
 